::Trinity::

Being the kitten that she was, she decided to go out and play. After all, a 
predacon sabertooth tiger kitten needs to stretch her legs once in a while.  
She went outside and started running into the dense underbush.  She was 
growling a kitten growl and having fun.  She saw a small butterfly and 
decided to chase it.  She swatted at it and  growled, trying to be as fierce 
as she could.  She ran about 4 miles before she stopped and looked around. 
She sat down and tried to get her barings. She hadn't payed attention to how 
she got there in the first place, so she had no idea how she got there.  She 
called out a kitten roar and hoped someone might help her back to her 
friends.
